					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5300603#post-3716263</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5300603/scp-3977#post-3716263</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2018 10:13:10 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>ModernMajorGeneral</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>274283</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Seconded, best of day 2. Well-written, disturbing and amusing all at once. I'm sure there are already a few articles which cover the 'commercial property in disturbing situation' but at the end of the day unoriginality is absolutely not something I could accuse this of.</p> <p>I would probably have enjoyed this more if I were familiar with the drink and commercials, but I don't think that's a fair criticism of the article.</p> <p>I was wondering if 'Dakkar' is meant to be Dakar, Senegal, or somewhere else, as I'm not sure if it's a misspelling or a variant.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
